Useful Swashbuckler Commands
----------------------------
sb, esb  - Talk to other Swashbucklers
swho     - See which Swashbucklers are online
stitle   - Set your title on the swho screen
srestore - Fix problems with your hat when not in town

endtech                    - End a technique earlier than normal
nameweapon <wpn> to <name> - Personalize your weapons
scheck                     - Check which techniques are in use

sbhelp new    - Shows recent changes to the guild
sbhelp styles - Quick reference file for blade styles

sbhelp general - More in-depth guild information, including skills
sbhelp skills  - A list of skills and their costs (included in 'general')
sbhelp titles  - Shows titles for all guild levels
sbhelp emotes  - Shows Swashbuckler emotes
